      <title>日本央行本周意外削减债券购买量，加息预期升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/boj-s-surprise-cut-to-bond-buying-this-week-fuels-rate-hike-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日本央行在本周的常规操作中意外减少了债券购买规模，投资者加大了对日本央行在 7 月份加息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/boj-s-surprise-cut-to-bond-buying-this-week-fuels-rate-hike-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 04:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国表示需要采取行动，德国则悄然采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/france-germany-rift-damages-european-union-s-ability-to-act-coherently</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克龙的宏伟计划和对肖尔茨的攻击掩盖了这样一个事实：在法国停滞不前的情况下，柏林正在加强对乌克兰的接触。]]></description>
